name: MOUNTAIN DOGU
description:
#01/07 of DOGU - White Series

This one was the first DOGU I ever drew. As an original one, the very first DOGU ever, he is dear to my heart. Let him be your guide in the journey through the world of DOGU.

The White Series focuses on combining old nature pictures with the DOGUs. This is an introduction to their world. Kind of like postcards from their land.

This series consists of 6 DOGUs and one secret DOGU.
